title: Week 13 Studs & Duds + Monday Punday, Javonte’s Inferno - Fantasy Football Podcast for 12/6
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode after a wild weekend of football! On today’s fantasy football podcast, get a recap of the biggest Studs & Duds of Week 13! Which performances are the most surprising and the most worrisome as the fantasy football playoffs approach? Plus, injury updates and Monday Punday! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for December 6th, 2021.
  
 (04:15) - Monday Punday
 (07:10) - NFL News 
 (15:30) - Fantasy Studmuffins
 (16:15) - QB Studs
 (20:10) - RB Studs
 (31:25) - WR Studs
 (38:00) - TE Studs
 (42:40) - Fantasy Duds
 (42:50) - QB Duds
 (49:20) - RB Duds

 (01:00:45) - TE Duds
